description.narrative: Government's capacity to manage Infant Young Child Feeding and micronutrient interventions was strengthened through the first 1000 days package, through setting up the SUN II programme. Service delivery was enhanced through procurement of 6,362,000 vitamin A capsules for supplementation reaching 3,375,072 children aged 6 to 59 months, sustaining service delivery points for IYCF. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:30/06/2020
